ResearchProjectDef.description:
Acquire knowledge of fleshmass cyst creation and new operations for mutating fleshmass organs from cyst.

Unlocks:
- Recipe to incubate fleshmass cyst;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass stomach;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass lung;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass liver;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass acid gland;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass nose.

Acquire knowledge of fleshmass tumor incubation operation and new operations for mutating fleshmass organs from tumor.

Unlocks:
- Operation to incubate fleshmass tumor;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass acid cavity;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass ear;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass eye;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass kidney;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass heart;
- Operation to incubate fleshmass brain tumor.
